  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Economy Double Rooms </strong>come with a king-size bed, air conditioning, satellite TV, safe, minibar, hairdryer and wifi. They’re decorated in a simple, Tuscan style and are ideal for a short stay.</p>
